    "And the formulation for most metrics can be easily extended to a multi-class scenario.",
    "This will enable generalizing the current study to the multi-class setting.",
    "For a one-versus-rest comparison, we expect similar results to hold, while for one-versus-one pairwise comparison, we expect similar results to hold conditional on the relative size of other classes not in the comparison.",
